{"id": 1785, "genre": 1001, "title": "王者荣耀限制未成年人游戏时间，你有什么话想说？", "description": "还有这种操作？！（题图来自林小妖）", "record_count": 3775, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170705101701kvoOWNpm8yd4lAIb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-05T03:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 219392, "content": "不知道为什么，德国的应用商店里没有王者荣耀可以下载...，为什么呢？只坑中国孩子？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660702}, {"id": 219648, "content": "我觉得没什么大用，真要想玩，哥哥姐姐爸爸妈妈的号都可以拿来玩，主要还是看自己，或者家长的监督力度（对于小学生队友", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070809}, {"id": 219904, "content": "表示不感兴趣???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963156}, {"id": 219393, "content": "去泥煤的农药梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071333}, {"id": 225281, "content": "我觉得应该限制，还要包括成年人。头脑中的不理性，有时候都会让我沉迷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090347}, {"id": 227841, "content": "活似一颗毒药", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098607}, {"id": 219394, "content": "表示昨天刚把游戏卸载。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070351}, {"id": 219650, "content": "没玩过，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040349}, {"id": 219395, "content": "我上小学的时候dnf就有防沉迷，然卵，第一天我就不知道在哪搜了张身份证号给过了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064756}, {"id": 219651, "content": "腾讯的当务之急是提高全国小学生的游戏水平。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070815}, {"id": 219907, "content": "中国式监管，表面一套，里面一套，都不玩怎么挣钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904362}, {"id": 221187, "content": "哈哈哈哈 王者这剂毒药", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076952}, {"id": 219652, "content": "与其只禁止孩子  不如全部禁止\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068239}, {"id": 220164, "content": "这做法根本没卵用，想玩的可以另外创小号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074282}, {"id": 224516, "content": "好样的，2亿国人玩那傻不拉几的游戏，痛心啊~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086467}, {"id": 228356, "content": "白日梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589122}, {"id": 219397, "content": "没有自制力的人不沉迷于王者荣耀也会沉迷于别的东西，跟游戏没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057148}, {"id": 219653, "content": "表示已经从坑里走了出来?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922699}, {"id": 219398, "content": "不知道 反正农药不好玩（摊手）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069400}, {"id": 219654, "content": "不如全部禁止  无法分辨未成年人与成年人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068239}, {"id": 219910, "content": "第一，王者荣耀会上瘾吗？第二，成人与未成年人哪类人的自制力强些？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071808}, {"id": 220166, "content": "感觉挺好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074362}, {"id": 219399, "content": "没玩过，没玩过，没玩过", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 219655, "content": "那么多人没玩过吗，真是厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499859}, {"id": 220167, "content": "感觉挺好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074362}, {"id": 219400, "content": "没玩过，没玩过，没玩过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 219912, "content": "抄袭的电视剧会被骂，抄袭的游戏却这么火", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066497}, {"id": 219401, "content": "表示我是dota控", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056696}, {"id": 219913, "content": "支持", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070169}, {"id": 220169, "content": "你们在骂小学生坑的时候忘记了，除了他们坑你的时候还有坑对面的时候。总结只有失去了才懂得珍惜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983300}, {"id": 219402, "content": "就跟以前防沉迷。。。就用爸妈的号或者身份证啊，没用的。。再说限制小学生也不太影响真正的收入来源?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050459}, {"id": 219914, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063522}, {"id": 219403, "content": "如图", "image": "img/option/option/2017070514540019aEs4pl0ui6NnIJ.png", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061932}, {"id": 219659, "content": "只想说不懂这个游戏有什么好玩的  无聊炸了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951314}, {"id": 219404, "content": "不可避免，只要他有这个心，用父母的身份证申请注册不是一样的吗？商家本来要做的，就是保持可持续的吸引力以适应市场，达到盈利目的。所以才不断更新，只能说针对未成年人自制力不够，且处于学习的关键期，这是一种缓解措施，却不能够从根本上改变问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054426}, {"id": 219660, "content": "所以，这样就成你掉段的理由？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811852}, {"id": 221708, "content": "真的，别玩游戏，要玩就玩健康的，游戏意义能让你放松，的不需要什么成就感，对生活的你没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078063}, {"id": 219661, "content": "如果不推出脸部识别或者虹膜识别和指纹认证登陆游戏，单靠身份证限制是行不通的，不过是腾讯应付舆论压力的手段罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017338}, {"id": 219918, "content": "王者榮耀這種廝殺類遊戲確實對小孩影響不好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712407}, {"id": 222479, "content": "高中不敢玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081210}, {"id": 219664, "content": "腾讯有责任和义务去增强企业自身管理，约束他人，尤其是青少年，将会为社会做出极大的贡献", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069618}, {"id": 219920, "content": "干得漂亮，要知道，离开这个游戏越早，你的人生越幸福～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911122}, {"id": 220432, "content": "自作自受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071459}, {"id": 221968, "content": "好玩的游戏还很多，为何沉迷王者？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078738}, {"id": 219665, "content": "95后，说实话真没碰过任何游戏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785639}, {"id": 220177, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074432}, {"id": 219411, "content": "腾讯出了游戏，玩不玩是你自己的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070403}, {"id": 219668, "content": "根据固然无可厚非，然而国家对于电子游戏的污化态度让人心寒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394508}, {"id": 219413, "content": "搞得限制玩游戏时间小盆友大盆友的学习成绩就能提高了一样。【虽然我不玩游戏】", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063946}, {"id": 219414, "content": "一次也没玩过的外星人路过！我就看着你们撕！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062133}]}